    {
      "id": "63c1916e7c7bff001ea5dd50",
      "text": "音律の歴史",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630064
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e52",
      "text": "from [/villagepump/音律の歴史]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e53",
      "text": "音律の歴史",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e54",
      "text": "\t[ピタゴラス音律]の発明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e55",
      "text": "\t　紀元前580〜500年ごろ、[ピタゴラス]が「弦の長さを3:2にした時、響きも美しい」と発見する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e56",
      "text": "　キリスト教がピタゴラス音階を宗教音楽に採用、普及する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630070
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e5a",
      "text": "　11世紀〜15世紀に[多声音楽]([ポリフォニー])が発展",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e5b",
      "text": "　\tピタゴラス音階では響きの悪いところがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e5c",
      "text": "　[純正律]の発明 バルトロメ・ラモス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e5d",
      "text": "　　ピタゴラス音階で響きの悪いところを響きのいい組み合わせにずらしたもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e5e",
      "text": "　　純正律では大全音 (9/8) と小全音 (10/9) の2種類の全音が存在する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e5f",
      "text": "　1636年 [平均律]の発明 マラン・[メルセンヌ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e60",
      "text": "\t\t均等な幅の半音12個で音階を形成",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e61",
      "text": "\t\t整数比で響きが美しいことよりも数学的な美しさを重視",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e62",
      "text": "\t　ド#とレ♭が同じ音になった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e63",
      "text": "\t\t弦の調律なしに転調が可能になった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673630062,
      "updated": 1673630062
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1916eaff09e0000324e64",
